com.netcracker.tc.model
Class Scenario

java.lang.Object
  com.netcracker.tc.model.Scenario

public class Scenario
extends Object

Atomic test step, describes test scenario, that has input parameters and output results. Belongs to one test case. Each step has some prototype Schema, that describes parameters and result that can have this step.

Author:
Aleksej Dsiuba
